text: Prainea is a genus of trees in the plant family Moraceae that is native to Southeast Asia. It is sometimes treated as a subgenus of Artocarpus. ==Species== *Prainea frutescens *Prainea limpato *Prainea microcephala *Prainea scandens ==References== Category:Moraceae Category:Moraceae genera
title: Prainea
